001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.types;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonSubTypes;
004import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonTypeInfo;
005import java.lang.Long;
006import java.lang.String;
007import java.time.OffsetDateTime;
008
009/**
010 * Versioned object have an ID and version and modification. Every update of this object changes it's version.
011 */
012@JsonTypeInfo(
013    use = JsonTypeInfo.Id.NAME,
014    include = JsonTypeInfo.As.PROPERTY,
015    property = "__typename"
016)
017@JsonSubTypes({
018    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = AssociateRole.class, name = "AssociateRole"),
019    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = AttributeGroup.class, name = "AttributeGroup"),
020    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = BusinessUnit.class, name = "BusinessUnit"),
021    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Cart.class, name = "Cart"),
022    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = CartDiscount.class, name = "CartDiscount"),
023    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Category.class, name = "Category"),
024    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Channel.class, name = "Channel"),
025    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = CommercetoolsSubscription.class, name = "CommercetoolsSubscription"),
026    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = CustomObject.class, name = "CustomObject"),
027    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Customer.class, name = "Customer"),
028    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = CustomerEmailToken.class, name = "CustomerEmailToken"),
029    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = CustomerGroup.class, name = "CustomerGroup"),
030    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = CustomerPasswordToken.class, name = "CustomerPasswordToken"),
031    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = DiscountCode.class, name = "DiscountCode"),
032    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Extension.class, name = "Extension"),
033    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = InventoryEntry.class, name = "InventoryEntry"),
034    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Message.class, name = "Message"),
035    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Order.class, name = "Order"),
036    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = OrderEdit.class, name = "OrderEdit"),
037    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Payment.class, name = "Payment"),
038    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Product.class, name = "Product"),
039    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = ProductDiscount.class, name = "ProductDiscount"),
040    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = ProductSelection.class, name = "ProductSelection"),
041    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = ProductTypeDefinition.class, name = "ProductTypeDefinition"),
042    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Quote.class, name = "Quote"),
043    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = QuoteRequest.class, name = "QuoteRequest"),
044    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Review.class, name = "Review"),
045    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = ShippingMethod.class, name = "ShippingMethod"),
046    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = ShoppingList.class, name = "ShoppingList"),
047    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = StagedQuote.class, name = "StagedQuote"),
048    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = StandalonePrice.class, name = "StandalonePrice"),
049    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = State.class, name = "State"),
050    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Store.class, name = "Store"),
051    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = TaxCategory.class, name = "TaxCategory"),
052    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = TypeDefinition.class, name = "TypeDefinition"),
053    @JsonSubTypes.Type(value = Zone.class, name = "Zone")
054})
055public interface Versioned {
056  String getId();
057
058  void setId(String id);
059
060  Long getVersion();
061
062  void setVersion(Long version);
063
064  OffsetDateTime getCreatedAt();
065
066  void setCreatedAt(OffsetDateTime createdAt);
067
068  OffsetDateTime getLastModifiedAt();
069
070  void setLastModifiedAt(OffsetDateTime lastModifiedAt);
071
072  Initiator getCreatedBy();
073
074  void setCreatedBy(Initiator createdBy);
075
076  Initiator getLastModifiedBy();
077
078  void setLastModifiedBy(Initiator lastModifiedBy);
079}
